snippet: The government says its criminal case against a former Blackwater security guard is in jeopardy as a June 11 trial looms on charges stemming from the shootings of dozens of Iraqi citizens in an incident in Baghdad nearly seven years ago....

headline.print_headline: Gov't: Case Against a Blackwater Guard in Jeopardy
headline.main: Gov't: Case Against a Blackwater Guard in Jeopardy

lead_paragraph: The government says its criminal case against a former Blackwater security guard is in jeopardy as a June 11 trial looms on charges stemming from the shootings of dozens of Iraqi citizens in an incident in Baghdad nearly seven years ago.
